description:
Expand your song library with an ever-growing list of hits and access more online features with the VIP Pass! 

The Let's Sing VIP Pass is an online subscription service that gives you access to an extensive and ever-growing online library of songs, more online multiplayer options and year-round seasonal events that are part of the Let's Sing Music Awards for one month. 

No automatic renewal.
This product is not sold on its own.
name: Let's Sing 2024 VIP Pass - Free Trial
